3
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:22,000
For instance, Phyllis, it must have been very difficult for you to part with this dented can of water chestnuts.

4
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:25,000
Well, they're good in stir-fries.

5
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:27,000
